== Trivia ==

* Earmuff Mode was originally called "Conversation Dome" during development
* This feature can also be quickly toggled by double-clicking the Audio tab, when the Quick Menu is open
* Concept art of Earmuff Mode showed [[VRCat]] wearing earmuffs, and without wearing their signature cardboard box; this was later changed to include the box

